{"word":"δέκατος","slug":"δέκατος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>δέϰατος, η, ον</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:δέκα\">δέκα</a></el>] <b><i>tenth</i><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> in a series, chronologically <b><a href='B:500 1:39'>J 1:39</a>; <a href='B:510 19:9'>Ac 19:9</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> partitively: <el>τὀ δέϰατον τῆς πόλεως</el> <i>a</i> <i>tenth of the city</i> <b><a href='B:730 11:13'>Rv 11:13</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ spec.\">spec.</a> as noun in cultic context, <el>ἡ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:δεκάτη\">δεκάτη</a></el> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ sc.\">sc.</a> <el>μέρις</el>) = part of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> offered as a gift, <i>tithe</i> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ sg.\">sg.</a> <b><a href='B:650 7:2'>Hb 7:2</a>, <a href='B:650 7:4'>4</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pl.\">pl.</a> <b><a href='B:650 7:8'>7:8f</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:δεκάτη\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:δεκατόω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}